This is a project to automate tests of list.am website.
Here is a short description for each folder:
    Helpers - In which all necessary helpers are described with loggers inside them. 
    Pages -  In which all necessary xpaths and methods to work those xpaths are written
    Tests - In which the following two test scenarios are covered: 
            Scenario 1
                1. Navigate to list.am
                2. Search by the word "house"
                3. Filter by Currency with USD and Price with 0-50 $
                4. Click on the blue icon
                5. Check that result's prices are within the filtered range

            Scenario 2
                1. Navigate to list.am
                2. Try add random item as favorite
                3. System show popup for required login

To run this project use command pytest <filename> or just pytest
